    "description": "Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag - Maximum organization, thermal protection and premium materials for demanding players. In modern padel, having well-organized and protected equipment is key to fully enjoying the game. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 has been designed as an advanced solution for players looking for a high-level racket bag that combines capacity, practicality and good organization for their gear.. This model stands out for its optimized structure with two independent thermal compartments, one on each side, a large central space for equipment and specific solutions to keep each item in perfect condition, such as its ventilated pocket for damp clothing. In terms of aesthetics, the blue design with bronze details provides a modern and distinctive style both on and off the court.. Made with next-generation technical materials, this racket bag not only guarantees durability, but also protection against moisture and weather conditions, making it an ideal option for players who demand performance in every aspect of their equipment.. Technical Features of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 has been developed to offer efficient space distribution, allowing two rackets to be transported isolated from extreme temperatures thanks to its thermal compartments, clothing and large accessories in the main compartment and damp clothing in the ventilated pocket. Let’s take a look at its features in full:. Brand: Adidas. Model: Protour Blue. Season: 2026. Bag type: Racket bag. Color: Blue with bronze details. Capacity: Medium, with space for up to 2 rackets. Dimensions: 42 x 60 x 30 cm. Materials: 100% REC. PES 900D with TPU coating + 100% REC. PES 210D + raincover. Compartments: Main compartment for equipment, 2 side thermal compartments for rackets, ventilated pocket for damp clothing and top pocket with velvet lining. Design: Ergonomic structure with padded handles and comfortable carrying system. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Racket Bag. Technical Fabric REC. PES 900D with TPU Coating: Maximum resistance and protection. This racket bag has been made with high-density recycled polyester (REC. PES 900D), a material especially resistant to wear, abrasion and intensive use. In addition, it incorporates a TPU coating that acts as a protective barrier against moisture, splashes and adverse weather conditions.. The use of REC. PES 210D inside allows for lightness without compromising resistance, while the raincover adds an extra layer of protection in situations of rain or high humidity.. Double Thermal Compartment: Protection for your rackets. The Adidas Protour Blue integrates two independent thermal compartments, located on both sides of the racket bag, designed to protect the rackets from temperature changes. Each of these compartments allows the storage of one racket, ensuring balanced distribution and optimal protection.. This system helps preserve the properties of the racket materials, preventing heat or cold from affecting their performance and extending their lifespan.. Main compartment and optimized organization. The central compartment offers a large space to transport clothing, towels and accessories, allowing everything to be kept organized and accessible. Its design facilitates efficient distribution of the equipment, ideal for players looking for practicality in their daily routine.. Ventilated pocket: separation of damp clothing. The racket bag incorporates an independent ventilated pocket designed for damp or used clothing, preventing the accumulation of moisture and bad odors in the rest of the equipment. This solution improves hygiene and organization after training sessions or intense matches by not mixing clean clothing with post-match clothing. Top pocket with velvet lining: protection for personal items. At the top, it includes a pocket with velvet lining, designed to protect delicate items such as mobile phones, glasses or personal accessories. This detail adds extra care and reinforces the premium character of the product.. Ergonomic carrying system. The design of the Adidas Protour Blue incorporates padded handles and ergonomic structure that allow the racket bag to be carried comfortably and in a balanced way. The weight distribution with backpack-style straps makes it easier to move around, even when the racket bag is fully loaded.. Who is this Adidas Protour Blue 2026 racket bag for?. This Adidas racket bag is designed for:. Demanding players looking for a racket bag with technical materials and great resistance.. Regular players who need to transport their equipment in an organized way.. Players who value the protection of their rackets through thermal compartments.. Players who prioritize modern design combined with advanced functionality.. Conclusion: Organization, protection and premium design in a single racket bag with the Adidas Protour 2026. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 represents the perfect balance between technology, capacity and design tailored for the modern player.. Thanks to its high-resistance materials, its independent thermal compartments, its optimized organization and its specific solutions for clothing and personal items, this racket bag guarantees a complete experience on and off the court.. If you are looking for a racket bag that combines protection, durability and style, the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 is an ideal option to take your equipment to the next level.",
