    "description": "Backpack Adidas PROTOUR Blue 2026 - Compact, durable and designed for efficient organization in every movement. Having a functional, comfortable and well-organized backpack is key to performing at your best in every training session or match. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 backpack presents itself as a compact and versatile solution for players who seek to transport their equipment in a practical and safe way.. This model stands out for its enhanced construction and its navy blue design with details in bronze and orange, providing a modern and distinctive aesthetic. In addition, it incorporates a U-shaped main opening that facilitates access to the contents, optimizing the user experience in daily use.. Thanks to its refined structure and high-quality technical materials, this backpack not only guarantees durability, but also excellent protection against moisture and greater comfort during movement, becoming an ideal option for players who seek performance and comfort.. Technical Features of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Backpack. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 has been designed to offer an intelligent distribution of space in a compact 40L format, allowing essential equipment to be transported comfortably and in an organized way. Let's take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Adidas. Model: Protour. Season: 2026. Bag Type: Backpack. Color: Navy blue with details in bronze and orange. Capacity: 40L, with space for one racket. Dimensions: 32 x 50 x 23 cm. Materials: 100% recycled polyester 900D with PU coating + 100% recycled polyester 210D. Compartments: Main compartment with U-shaped opening, internal thermal pocket for one racket, ventilated lower compartment for wet clothes or footwear and additional pockets for accessories. Design: Padded back panel, compact and ergonomic structure for daily use. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Protour Blue 2026 Backpack. Recycled 900D polyester with PU coating: Resistance and protection against moisture. This Adidas Protour backpack has been manufactured with 900D recycled polyester, a high-density fabric that offers great resistance to wear, friction and continuous use. In addition, it incorporates a PU coating that acts as a protective barrier against moisture and splashes.. The use of 210D recycled polyester inside allows maintaining a light weight without compromising durability, achieving a perfect balance between resistance, functionality and sustainability.. Internal thermal pocket: Additional protection for your racket. Inside, the backpack incorporates a thermal insulated pocket designed to protect the racket from temperature changes, helping to preserve its properties for a longer time.. This type of thermal linings is highly valued by professional players since on one hand, it offers the advantage of keeping your racket insulated from very cold or very hot temperatures during transport to the court and guaranteeing its performance for the match and on the other hand, it helps to keep it protected from temperature changes, maintaining its properties for longer.. Ventilated lower compartment: Separation of wet clothes or footwear. The backpack integrates a ventilated lower compartment that allows separating wet clothes or footwear from the rest of the equipment. This solution prevents the accumulation of moisture and bad odors, improving hygiene and organization after intense training sessions or matches.. U-shaped opening and optimized organization. The U-shaped main opening facilitates quick and comfortable access to the interior of the backpack, allowing better visibility and organization of the contents. This design improves functionality and makes daily use easier.. Padded back panel: Greater comfort during movement. The padded back panel provides extra comfort during transport, adapting to the back and reducing pressure during movement. This feature is especially useful for players who frequently travel to training sessions or competitions.. Who is this Adidas Protour Blue 2026 backpack for?. This Adidas Protour backpack is designed for:. Players who are looking for a compact and functional backpack.. Regular players who need to transport their essential equipment in an organized way.. Players who value thermal protection for their racket or devices.. Players who prioritize comfort during their movements.. Players who are looking for a modern design with durable materials.. Conclusion: Organization, protection and comfort in a compact format. The Adidas Protour Blue 2026 backpack is an ideal option for those who are looking for a compact, durable and well-equipped backpack for daily use on the court.. Thanks to its optimized structure, its internal thermal pocket, its ventilated compartment and its ergonomic design, it guarantees efficient organization and proper protection of your equipment, allowing you to transport your racket, footwear and the necessary clothing for after your matches or training sessions. If you are looking for a backpack that combines functionality, durability and comfort, the Adidas Protour is the perfect choice to take to the court.",
