    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega Racket Bag - Organization, thermal protection and exclusive design for demanding players. In today’s padel, having well-organized and protected equipment is key to fully enjoying the padel experience. The Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega has been designed as an advanced solution for players looking for a high-level racket bag that combines capacity, practicality and excellent organization for their equipment.. This model, the same one used by professional player Marta Ortega, stands out for its optimized structure with two independent thermal compartments, one on each side, a large central space for equipment and a ventilated pocket for damp clothing. Its pink and black design with white details provides a modern, distinctive and clean style on and off the court.. Made with latest-generation technical materials, this racket bag not only guarantees durability, but also protection against humidity and weather conditions, making it an ideal option for players who demand performance in all aspects of their equipment.. Technical Features of the Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega Racket Bag. The Adidas Protour Pink 2026 has been developed to offer an efficient distribution of space, allowing you to carry two rackets, clothing and accessories without having to worry about leaving anything at home. Let’s take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Adidas. Model: Protour Pink. Season: 2026. Bag Type: Racket bag. Color: Pink and black with white details. Capacity: Medium, with space for up to 2 rackets. Dimensions: 42 x 60 x 30 cm. Materials: 100% REC. PES 900D with TPU coating + 100% REC. PES 210D + raincover. Compartments: Main compartment for equipment, 2 lateral thermal compartments for rackets, ventilated pocket for damp clothing and top pocket with velvet lining. Design: Ergonomic structure with padded handles and comfortable carrying system. Technologies and Materials of the Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega Racket Bag. REC. PES 900D Technical Fabric with TPU Coating: Maximum resistance and protection. This racket bag has been made with high-density recycled polyester (REC. PES 900D), a material especially resistant to wear, abrasion and intensive use. In addition, it incorporates a TPU coating that acts as a protective barrier against humidity, splashes and adverse weather conditions.. The use of REC. PES 210D on the inside allows maintaining lightness without compromising resistance, while the raincover adds an extra layer of protection in rainy or high-humidity conditions.. Double Thermal Compartment: Protection for your rackets. The Adidas Protour Pink integrates two independent thermal compartments, located on both sides of the bag, designed to protect rackets from temperature changes. Each of these compartments allows storing one racket, ensuring balanced distribution and optimal protection.. This system helps preserve the properties of racket materials, preventing heat or cold from affecting their performance and extending their lifespan.. Main compartment and optimized organization. The central compartment offers ample space to carry clothing, towels and accessories, allowing everything to remain organized and accessible. Its design facilitates efficient distribution of equipment, ideal for players who seek practicality in their daily routine.. Ventilated pocket: separation of damp clothing. The racket bag incorporates an independent ventilated pocket designed for damp or used clothing, preventing the accumulation of humidity and bad odors in the rest of the equipment. This solution improves hygiene and organization after training sessions or intense matches by not mixing clean clothes with post-match clothing.. Top pocket with velvet lining: protection for personal items. On the top, it includes a pocket with velvet lining, designed to protect delicate items such as mobile phone, glasses or personal accessories. This detail adds extra care and reinforces the premium character of the product.. Ergonomic carrying system. The design of the Adidas Protour Pink incorporates padded handles and ergonomic structure that allow carrying the bag comfortably and in a balanced way. The weight distribution with backpack-style straps makes transport easier, even when the bag is fully loaded.. Who is this Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega racket bag for?. This Adidas racket bag is designed for:. Demanding players looking for a bag with technical materials and great resistance.. Regular players who need to carry their equipment in an organized way.. Players who value the protection of their rackets through thermal compartments.. Fans of Marta Ortega who want to equip themselves with the same gear as a professional player.. Players who prioritize modern design combined with advanced functionality.. Conclusion: Exclusive design, protection for your equipment and comfortable transport with the Adidas Protour Pink by Marta Ortega. The Adidas Protour Pink 2026 Marta Ortega represents the perfect balance between technology, capacity and design tailored for the modern player.. Thanks to its high-resistance materials, its independent thermal compartments, its optimized organization and its specific solutions for clothing and personal items, this racket bag guarantees a complete experience on and off the court.. If you are looking for a racket bag that combines protection, durability and style, the Adidas Protour Pink 2026 is an ideal option to take your equipment to the next level with the support of Marta Ortega.",
