    "description": "Babolat Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron 2025 Racket – Professional Padel Racket for Technical Attackers. The Babolat Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron 2025 represents the ultimate expression of power and offensive dominance in professional padel. Developed in close collaboration with Juan Lebron, one of the best players in the world, this racket has been designed for players who seek not only explosive performance but also cutting-edge technology to make a difference in every point. Its conception responds to the demands of the modern game, where speed, precision and control are essential elements.. With an innovative design and premium materials, the Viper 2.5 combines a robust construction with perfect balance to enhance every attacking shot, whether at the net or from the baseline. This Babolat padel racket is not just a piece of equipment, but a symbol of the aggressive and technical character that defines Juan Lebron’s style, giving every player the confidence needed to execute decisive shots. Its diamond shape and high balance make this racket a lethal weapon for attacking play.. The Babolat Technical Viper Juan Lebron incorporates the brand’s latest innovations, including the revolutionary Dynamic Stability System, the practical Smart Buttcap, and the rough surface with 3D Spin+ technology, all working together to deliver an unmatched playing experience.. If you are looking for a Babolat racket that combines explosive power, exceptional control and the prestige of being used by a world champion, the Viper Juan Lebron 2025 is your perfect choice.. Technical Specifications of the Babolat Viper Juan Lebron. The Babolat Viper Juan Lebron is designed for players who prioritize power in their shots without sacrificing technical control. Its diamond shape and high balance concentrate the weight in the head to enhance impact strength, making it ideal for smashes and attacking shots. This feature makes it especially suitable for advanced and professional players who want to dominate the court with powerful strokes.. Brand: Babolat. Model: Viper 2.5. Year: 2025. Shape: Diamond. Balance: High. Weight: 370g. Core: X-EVA. Faces: 3K Carbon. Surface: Rough. Level of Play: Professional / Advanced. Type of Play: Power. Features and Technologies of the Babolat Viper 2.5. 3K Carbon. The 3K Carbon fiber is one of the most advanced materials used in the manufacture of high-end padel rackets. It consists of carbon fiber woven with a specific pattern of 3000 filaments per square centimeter, providing an exceptional balance between strength, lightness and rigidity. In the Viper Juan Lebron, this technology guarantees maximum explosiveness in every shot, with outstanding precision even at high speeds. It also enhances the racket’s durability, maintaining its properties over time.. The stiffer outer layers of 3K carbon provide the structure needed to withstand intense impacts without losing rigidity or precision. This is essential for players who need an aggressive weapon at the net while maintaining control in technical and placement shots. The use of this material in the Babolat Viper padel racket ensures high quality and professional performance.. Dynamic Stability System. The Dynamic Stability System is an exclusive design integrated into the heart of the racket, featuring a reinforced central bar that improves stability during impact. This technology reduces vibrations, providing greater comfort while also increasing power and control. Thanks to this system, attacking shots become more decisive, allowing players to maintain intensity and accuracy without losing precision or causing muscle fatigue.. This system is especially valued by professional players like Juan Lebron, who require equipment that performs optimally under high pressure. It ensures every shot feels solid and controlled, boosting confidence in critical match situations.. Smart Buttcap. The Smart Buttcap system is an innovative handle design that allows the safety strap to be removed quickly and easily. This makes cleaning and maintenance easier, as well as enabling players to change the strap according to their preferences. Although it may seem like a small detail, it offers significant practical value, ensuring the racket is always ready to deliver optimal performance.. 3D Spin+ Surface. The racket features a rough surface called 3D Spin+, designed to improve spin generation on the ball. This special texture enhances shots such as the vibora, smash by 3 or bandeja, making them more difficult to return and increasing effectiveness in offensive situations.. The rough finish with relief not only enhances spin but also improves ball grip at impact, resulting in greater precision and control. This technology is particularly useful for smashes and attacking shots, where added spin can make the difference between winning a point or facing a return.. X-EVA Core. The core of the racket is made of high-density EVA rubber, known as X-EVA, constructed in three layers. The outer layers of medium density provide a firm yet comfortable feel, enabling powerful shots while maintaining comfort and vibration reduction. The standard 38 mm thickness ensures an ideal balance between rigidity and flexibility, preserving maneuverability and power.. The inner layer guarantees optimal response in all playing situations, from defensive shots to explosive attacks. This core is ideal for players seeking power without compromising comfort.. Holes Pattern System. The optimized hole distribution, developed through the Holes Pattern System, maximizes power and precision in every shot. It improves aerodynamics, reduces unnecessary weight and enhances ball control, especially in aggressive and high-speed shots, which is essential for an offensive player like Juan Lebron.. Who Is the Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron For?. The Babolat Viper Juan Lebron 2025 is specifically designed for professional and advanced players looking for a high-power racket oriented towards attacking play. It is perfect for:. Professional or advanced players seeking high power.. Technical attackers who want to dominate the court with aggressive and precise shots.. Players requiring excellent stability and exceptional control.. Those looking for advanced technologies to maximize spin.. Players who value an exclusive design inspired by Juan Lebron.. Conclusion: The Babolat Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron 2025 – The Ultimate Weapon for Technical Attackers. The Babolat Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron 2025 perfectly combines advanced technology, exclusive design and outstanding on-court performance. Built for offensive and technical players, it stands out for its explosive power, stability and spin potential, elevating your game to the highest level.. If you are looking for a Babolat racket that allows you to dominate every point with power and precision, the Babolat Viper 2.5 Juan Lebron is your definitive choice for the 2025 season.. This product cannot be shipped outside the European Union.",
