    "description": "HEAD COELLO PRO X Pádel ARTURO COELLO – Exclusive design, performance and sustainability. Designed with “King Arturo” in mind. The HEAD COELLO PRO X Pádel Backpack was developed in collaboration with champion Arturo Coello, combining elite performance, sustainability and standout design. Signature details like the crown logo on the front and strap make this backpack visually distinctive and collectible.. The vibrant red interior reflects Coello’s favorite color, while the silver HEAD logo on the black exterior adds a touch of elegance and identity.. Eco-conscious construction. Made from recycled materials, it features 50% rPET, 47% PU and 3% nylon on the exterior, and 100% rPET inside. A recycled paper tag with hemp string reinforces HEAD’s commitment to sustainability.. Smart storage layout. A padded compartment for two racquets ensures protection. The main compartment opens wide for easy access, while internal organizers and a zipped front pocket keep essentials in order.. Functional for everyday use. A separate shoe compartment keeps footwear apart from clean gear. The side mesh pocket holds a water bottle or quick-access items. This is the perfect backpack for both match days and urban commutes.",
