    "sourceProductId": "42722756597",
    "sourceCategory": "Tennis",
    "description": "HEAD Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 Racket Bag - Padel racket bag for players who value organization and great capacity with Coello’s endorsement. In the world of padel, having the right equipment is essential to maximize performance and comfort during every training session or match. The HEAD Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 is presented as a comprehensive solution for the most demanding players looking for a racket bag that combines advanced functionality, notable capacity and a modern and attractive design.. Manufactured to meet the demands of athletes, this racket bag stands out for its versatility and for incorporating exclusive technologies that guarantee the optimal protection and organization of your equipment, such as the CCT+ technology to keep your rackets insulated from temperature changes, the integrated compartment for footwear or its additional pockets for accessories.. The edition of the Coello Tour Padel Bag in black with red details not only offers an elegant and contemporary style, but also incorporates latest generation fabrics, a red interior that reflects the player’s style and an ergonomic transport system that makes carrying easier without sacrificing comfort. This racket bag is designed to accompany you in every match and training session, ensuring that all your equipment is protected and organized so you can access it comfortably and quickly at all times.. Technical Features of the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 Racket Bag. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 racket bag stands out for its large capacity in which you can carry up to a total of 7 rackets thanks to its 3 compartments, one of them with CCT+ protection (Climate Control Plus) to protect the rackets from extreme temperatures and temperature changes. On the other hand, the integrated shoe compartment stands out so you can carry your clothing separate from footwear and avoid unwanted stains. Let’s take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Head. Model: Coello Tour Padel Bag. Season: 2025. Bag Type: Racket bag. Color: Black with red details and red interior. Capacity: 40 L with space for up to 7 rackets. Dimensions: 60 X 28.5 X 36.5 cm. Materials: 80% Polyester, 20% PU. Compartments: 3 main compartments, one of them with CCT+ technology, integrated shoe compartment and a total of 4 pockets for accessories, three external and one internal.. Design: Padded top handles, ergonomic design to carry it as a backpack, red interior and Coello crown logos in red distributed throughout the bag. Technologies and Materials of the Head Coello Tour 2025 Racket Bag. Exclusive Arturo Coello design with red details and crown logo. One of the most outstanding features of the HEAD Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 is its exclusive design developed in collaboration with professional player Arturo Coello. Its exterior finish in black with red details, the red interior and the integration of the Coello crown logo in red in various parts of the bag provide a unique, modern and easily recognizable aesthetic both on and off the court.. High-Resistance Fabrics: Polyester and Polyurethane. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag racket bag has been manufactured with a combination of 80% polyester and 20% polyurethane (PU) that ensures optimal resistance against wear, abrasion and exposure to weather conditions. Polyester provides durability and lightness, while polyurethane offers partial waterproofing and greater protection against moisture and stains.. CCT+ Technology (Climate Control Temperature Plus). The CCT + technology is one of the technologies that stand out the most in this Head racket bag aimed at advanced equipment protection. This technology consists of thermal insulation and temperature regulation designed to protect padel rackets from sudden temperature changes that can negatively affect their performance and durability.. The CCT+ compartment helps to keep rackets in optimal condition, preventing their materials from being affected by excessive heat or intense cold. This technology is only found in one of the main compartments, so you can carry your favorite rackets more protected.. Highly Functional Compartments and Pockets. The HEAD Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 is equipped with three main compartments that allow you to carry up to seven rackets, an ideal capacity for players who use different models or who want to have spare rackets at hand.. On the other hand, it features two large external pockets with zippers to store accessories such as grips, balls or other essential items, an external pocket specially designed for the mobile phone providing quick and safe access and a final internal pocket with zipper for other accessories or personal items that you want to keep more secure.. Integrated Shoe Compartment. The inclusion of an independent compartment for shoes is a feature that demonstrates attention to detail and understanding of the player’s needs. This separate space prevents dirt from the shoes and odors from mixing with the rest of the equipment, maintaining proper hygiene and reinforcing the great capacity and functionality with which this racket bag has been designed.. Ergonomic Backpack-Style Transport System. To facilitate the transport of the bag, HEAD has integrated a system of backpack-style straps that distribute the weight evenly across the shoulders and back. These padded and adjustable straps adapt to different body shapes and carrying preferences. This ergonomic solution reduces fatigue during transport and improves mobility.. Environmental Commitment: Recycled Materials and Sustainable Labeling. Beyond functionality, HEAD demonstrates a strong commitment to sustainability. The hanging tag of the bag is made from recycled paper and attached with a hemp cord, and the protective cover in which the bag is delivered is made of recycled plastic, reinforcing the brand’s ecological commitment.. Who is this Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 racket bag for?. This Head Coello Tour Padel Bag racket bag is designed for:. Players who require large and organized storage for their equipment.. High-level players who need to carry several rackets to be able to play with different playing styles or simply have spare rackets available.. Advanced players who know how important it is to protect their rackets from temperature changes and value technologies such as CCT+.. Players who are looking for a modern and elegant design with an exclusive identity inspired by Arturo Coello and value a bag with a distinctive aesthetic on the court.. Players who prioritize organization for their equipment and value that racket bags include a specific compartment for shoes, accessory pockets and separate compartments for rackets.. Fans of Arturo Coello who want to have the same equipment or reflect his style on the court.. Conclusion: Enjoy the complete padel experience with a large-capacity racket bag to carry everything you need with the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag. The HEAD Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 represents a perfect synthesis between technological innovation, capacity and design aimed at maximum performance and comfort for the padel player.. Thanks to its high-quality materials, its CCT+ climate control system and its intelligent distribution of compartments, this racket bag guarantees that each sports item remains protected and organized, facilitating the daily logistics of training and competition.. This Coello Tour Padel Bag is an outstanding option for those who value quality, advanced functionality and sustainable commitment in their sports products. It does not matter if you are an amateur player who trains occasionally or a competitor who demands the best for their equipment, this racket bag is designed to exceed your expectations. Do not miss this opportunity and get the Head Coello Tour Padel Bag 2025 to elevate the total padel experience and enjoy maximum comfort and protection for your equipment!",
