    "description": "Racket Bag HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Black - Racket Bag for players who value organization and large capacity. In the world of padel, having the right equipment is essential to maximize performance and comfort during every training session or competition. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Black is presented as a comprehensive solution for the most demanding players who are looking for a racket bag that combines advanced functionality, notable capacity and a modern and attractive design.. Manufactured to meet the demands of athletes, this racket bag stands out for its versatility and for incorporating exclusive technologies that guarantee the optimal protection and organization of your equipment, such as the CCT+ technology to keep your rackets insulated from temperature changes, the integrated compartment for footwear or its additional pockets for accessories.. The Tour Padel Bag L edition in black color not only offers an elegant and contemporary style, but also incorporates latest generation fabrics, including a reflective material that improves visibility in low light conditions, and an ergonomic transport system that makes it easy to carry without sacrificing comfort. This racket bag is designed to accompany you in every match and training session, ensuring that all your equipment is protected and organized to access it comfortably and quickly at all times.. Technical Features of the Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026. This racket bag Head Tour padel Bag L 2026 stands out for its large capacity in which you can carry up to a total of 7 rackets thanks to its 3 compartments, one of them with CCT+ protection (Climate Control Plus) to protect the rackets from extreme temperatures and temperature changes. On the other hand, the integrated compartment for footwear stands out so that you can carry your clothes separate from the shoes and avoid unwanted stains. Let’s take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Head. Model: Tour Padel Bag L. Season: 2026. Type of Bag: Racket Bag. Color: Black. Capacity: 40 L with space for up to 7 rackets. Dimensions: 60 X 28,5 X 36,5 cm. Materials: 90% Polyester, 10% PU. Compartments: 3 main compartments, one of them with CCT+ technology, integrated compartment for footwear and a total of 4 pockets for accessories, three external and one internal.. Design: Padded top handles and ergonomic design to carry it as a backpack. Technologies and Materials of the Head Tour L 2026 Racket Bag. High Visibility Reflective Material. One of the most outstanding innovations of the HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 is the incorporation of a reflective material in its outer composition. This advanced fabric significantly improves the visibility of the player during movement in low light conditions or at dusk, providing a modern and distinctive design compared to other racket bags on the market.. High Resistance Fabrics: Polyester and Polyurethane. This racket bag Head Tour Padel Bag L has been manufactured with a combination of 90% polyester and 10% polyurethane (PU) that ensures optimal resistance against wear, abrasion and exposure to weather conditions. Polyester provides durability and lightness, while polyurethane offers partial waterproofing and greater protection against moisture and stains.. CCT+ Technology (Climate Control Temperature Plus). The CCT + technology is one of the technologies that stand out the most in this Head racket bag focused on advanced equipment protection. This technology consists of a thermal insulation and temperature regulation designed to protect padel rackets from sudden temperature changes that can negatively affect their performance and durability.. The CCT+ compartment helps to keep the rackets in optimal conditions, preventing their materials from being affected by excessive heat or intense cold. This technology is only found in one of the main compartments, so you can carry your favorite rackets more protected.. High Functionality Compartments and Pockets. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 is equipped with three main compartments that allow you to carry up to seven rackets, an ideal capacity for players who use different models or who want to have spare rackets on hand.. On the other hand, it has two large external pockets with zippers to store accessories such as grips, balls or other essential items, an external pocket specially designed for the mobile phone allowing quick and safe access and a final internal zip pocket for other accessories or personal items that you want to keep safer.. Integrated Footwear Compartment. The inclusion of an independent compartment for shoes is a feature that demonstrates attention to detail and understanding of the player’s needs. This separate space prevents dirt from the shoes and odors from mixing with the rest of the equipment, maintaining proper hygiene and reinforcing the great capacity and functionality with which this racket bag has been designed.. Ergonomic Backpack Carrying System. To facilitate the transport of the bag, HEAD has integrated a system of backpack-style straps that distribute the weight evenly across the shoulders and back. These padded and adjustable straps adapt to different body types and transport preferences. This ergonomic solution reduces fatigue during transport and improves mobility.. Environmental Commitment: Recycled Materials and Sustainable Labeling. Beyond functionality, HEAD demonstrates a strong commitment to sustainability. The hanging tag of the bag is made from recycled paper and attached with a hemp cord, as well as the protective cover in which the bag is delivered is made of recycled plastic, reinforcing the brand’s ecological commitment.. Who is this Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026 for?. This Head Tour Padel Bag L racket bag is designed for:. Players who require spacious and organized storage for their equipment.. High-level players who need to carry several rackets to play with different styles or simply have spare rackets available.. Advanced players who know how important it is to protect their rackets from temperature changes and value technologies such as CCT+.. Players who are looking for a modern and elegant design and value the visibility elements that this bag incorporates for safer transport at night or in low light conditions.. Players who prioritize organization for their equipment and value that racket bags include a specific compartment for footwear, pockets for accessories and separate compartments for rackets.. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Black is especially suitable for players who are looking for a racket bag with large capacity and who train in different environmental conditions or compete in tournaments where equipment preservation is crucial.. Conclusion: Enjoy the complete padel experience with a large capacity bag to carry everything you need with the Head Tour Padel Bag L. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Black represents a perfect synthesis between technological innovation, capacity and design aimed at maximum performance and comfort for the padel player.. Thanks to its high-quality materials, its CCT+ climate control system and its intelligent distribution of compartments, this racket bag ensures that every piece of sports equipment remains protected and organized, facilitating the daily logistics of training and competition.. This Tour Padel Bag L is an outstanding option for those who value quality, advanced functionality and sustainable commitment in their sports products. Whether you are an amateur player who trains occasionally or a competitor who demands the best for their equipment, this bag is designed to exceed your expectations. Don’t miss this opportunity and get the Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026 to elevate the total padel experience and enjoy maximum comfort and protection for your equipment!",
