    "description": "Racket Bag HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Green/Orange - Padel Racket Bag for players who value organization and large capacity. In the world of padel, having the right equipment is essential to maximize performance and comfort during every training session or competition. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Green/Orange is presented as a comprehensive solution for the most demanding players who are looking for a racket bag that combines advanced functionality, notable capacity, and a modern and attractive design.. Manufactured to meet the demands of athletes, this racket bag stands out for its versatility and for incorporating exclusive technologies that guarantee the optimal protection and organization of your equipment, such as the CCT+ technology to keep your rackets insulated from temperature changes, the integrated shoe compartment or its additional pockets for accessories.. The edition of the Tour Padel Bag L in green and orange not only offers a fresh and contemporary style, but also incorporates next-generation fabrics, including a reflective material that improves visibility in low light conditions, and an ergonomic transport system that makes carrying easier without sacrificing comfort. This racket bag is designed to accompany you in every match and training session, ensuring that all your equipment is protected and organized to access it comfortably and quickly at all times.. Technical Features of the Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Racket Bag. This racket bag Head Tour padel Bag L 2026 stands out for its large capacity in which you can carry up to a total of 7 rackets thanks to its 3 compartments, one of them with CCT+ protection (Climate Control Plus) to protect the rackets from extreme temperatures and temperature changes. On the other hand, the integrated shoe compartment stands out so that you can carry your clothing separate from the footwear and avoid unwanted stains. Let’s take a closer look at its features:. Brand: Head. Model: Tour Padel Bag L. Season: 2026. Type of Bag: Racket Bag. Color: Green and Orange. Capacity: 40 L with space for up to 7 rackets. Dimensions: 60 X 28.5 X 36.5 cm. Materials: 80% Polyester, 20% PU. Compartments: 3 main compartments, one of them with CCT+ technology, integrated shoe compartment and a total of 4 accessory pockets, three external and one internal.. Design: Padded top handles and ergonomic design to carry it as a backpack. Technologies and Materials of the Head Tour L 2026 Racket Bag. High Visibility Reflective Material. One of the most notable innovations of the HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 is the incorporation of a reflective material in its outer composition. This advanced fabric significantly improves player visibility during movement in low light conditions or at dusk, while providing a modern and distinctive design compared to other racket bags on the market.. High Resistance Fabrics: Polyester and Polyurethane. This racket bag Head Tour Padel Bag L has been manufactured with a combination of 80% polyester and 20% polyurethane (PU) that ensures optimal resistance against wear, abrasion, and exposure to weather conditions. Polyester provides durability and lightness, while polyurethane offers partial waterproofing and greater protection against moisture and stains.. CCT+ Technology (Climate Control Temperature Plus). The CCT + technology is one of the most outstanding technologies in this Head racket bag aimed at advanced equipment protection. This technology consists of thermal insulation and temperature regulation designed to protect padel rackets from sudden temperature changes that can negatively affect their performance and durability.. The CCT+ compartment helps to keep rackets in optimal conditions, preventing their materials from being affected by excessive heat or intense cold. This technology is only found in one of the main compartments, so you can carry your favorite rackets more protected.. Highly Functional Compartments and Pockets. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 is equipped with three main compartments that allow carrying up to seven rackets, an ideal capacity for players who use different models or who want to have spare rackets on hand.. On the other hand, it has two large external pockets with zippers to store accessories such as grips, balls, or other essential items, an external pocket specially designed for the mobile phone allowing quick and secure access, and a final internal zip pocket for other accessories or personal items that you want to keep more secure.. Integrated Shoe Compartment. The inclusion of an independent compartment for shoes is a feature that demonstrates attention to detail and understanding of the player's needs. This separate space prevents dirt from the shoes and odors from mixing with the rest of the equipment, maintaining proper hygiene and reinforcing the great capacity and functionality with which this racket bag has been designed.. Ergonomic Backpack Carrying System. To facilitate the transport of the racket bag, HEAD has integrated a system of backpack straps that distribute the weight evenly across the shoulders and back. These padded and adjustable straps adapt to different body types and carrying preferences. This ergonomic solution reduces fatigue during transport and improves mobility.. Environmental Commitment: Recycled Materials and Sustainable Labeling. Beyond functionality, HEAD demonstrates a strong commitment to sustainability. The hanging tag of the racket bag is made of recycled paper and attached with a hemp cord, as well as the protective cover in which the racket bag is delivered is made of recycled plastic, reinforcing the brand’s ecological commitment.. Who is this Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Racket Bag for?. This Head Tour Padel Bag L racket bag is designed for:. Players who require ample and organized storage for their equipment.. High-level players who need to carry several rackets to play with different styles of play or simply have spare rackets available.. Advanced players who know how important it is to protect their rackets from temperature changes and value technologies such as CCT+.. Players who are looking for a modern design and value the visibility elements that this racket bag integrates for safer transport at night or in low light conditions.. Players who prioritize organization for their equipment and value that racket bags include a specific compartment for shoes, pockets for accessories, and separate compartments for rackets.. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Green/Orange is especially suitable for players who are looking for a racket bag with large capacity and who train in different environmental conditions or compete in tournaments where material preservation is crucial.. Conclusion: Enjoy the complete padel experience with a large-capacity racket bag to carry everything you need with the Head Tour Padel Bag L. The HEAD Tour Padel Bag L 2026 Green/Orange represents a perfect synthesis between technological innovation, capacity, and design aimed at maximum performance and comfort for the padel player.. Thanks to its high-quality materials, its CCT+ climate control system, and its intelligent distribution of compartments, this racket bag ensures that each piece of sports equipment remains protected and organized, facilitating the daily logistics of training and competition.. This Tour Padel Bag L is an outstanding option for those who value quality, advanced functionality, and sustainable commitment in their sports products. It doesn’t matter if you are an amateur player who trains occasionally or a competitor who demands the best for their equipment, this racket bag is designed to exceed your expectations. Don’t miss this opportunity and get the Head Tour Padel Bag L 2026 to elevate the total padel experience and enjoy maximum comfort and protection for your equipment!",
